data.title: Dealer Equipment & Services Program
data.text:
Click to view California Proposition 65 warning

Service cart to perform complete service of Kinetic® suspension system: Evacuation, Test, Degassing, Fill

Technical Specifications:

Hydraulic Filter Rating: 10 Micron

Humidity: 32.2˚C (90˚F), 80% RH non-condensing

Manometer: Ø 100 mm (3.9 in.)

Maximum Pressure: 35 bar (507 PSI)

Noise: <72 dB(A)

Nominal Voltage: KS59000 115V, 60 Hz

Air Consumption at Recommended Operating Pressure: 0.5 CFM

Recommended Operating Pressure: 65 – 150 PSI

Operating Temperature: 10˚C – 50˚C (50˚F – 122˚F)

Power Consumption: 1380 VA

Vacuum Pump Free-Air Displacement: 1.5 CFM (42 L/m) @ 60 Hz

Hydraulic Pump: 0.00081 g/r @ 1/2 hp, 1725 rpm, 120V 60 Hz

Service Hoses: 15 ft, ISO 18752-AC

Tank Capacity: New Fluid Tank - 5L, Waste Fluid Tank - 6L

Features

Evacuation: Pressure differential based.

Test: 55 PSI filtered, compressed air system pressure leak test.

Test: -28 inHg system vacuum leak test.

Fluid Degassing: 15 min degassing procedure at -28 inHg.

Fill: 30 Bar system pressurization fill procedure.

Dimensions: 1000 cm x 750 cm x 750 cm.

Display: 5 x 9 cm (4.3 in. diag) graphic LCD.

Manometer: Ø 100 mm (3.9 in.) - Maximum Pressure: 35 bar (507 PSI)

Noise: <72 dB(A) - Nominal Voltage: KS59000 115V, 60 Hz
